data.title: Tax Payer Details Reports
data.meta_description: TaxPayerDetailsReports(2) - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls / .xlsx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document contains a list of 57 companies or organizations registered in Gachibowli, Rangareddy district of Hyderabad, India. It includes their GSTIN registration numbers, legal names, and trade names. The registration type is listed as "ALL" and it is administered by the "Center".
